*emul-linux-x86-xlibs-1.1-r1 (17 Jul 2004)

  17 Jul 2004; Andrew Bevitt <cyfred@gentoo.org>;
  +emul-linux-x86-xlibs-1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixing LDPATH for new opengl-update; it will now handle 32bit GL libs

  14 Apr 2004; Danny van Dyk <kugelfang@gentoo.org> emul-linux-x86-xlibs-1.1.ebuild:
  Ebuild now adds /etc/env.d/75emul-linux-x86-xlibs "on the fly", I forgot to
  include that into the tarball. Fixes BUG #47773.
  Also fixed libxrx.so[.6] to be symlinks and not copies of libxrx.so.6.3. (Also BUG #47773)

  14 Apr 2004; Travis Tilley <lv@gentoo.org> emul-linux-x86-xlibs-1.1.ebuild:
  it seems xlibs 1.1 is broken for some people, so i'm going to mask it for now

